    <p><em>Last Updated: March 1, 2025</em></p>
    <p>At SuperCight Domains, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard data when you visit <em>Tree.Institute</em>—including its blog—or interact with our domain sales services.</p>
